      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was looking at some old street maps of dc last night and something just clicked. i started tracing the main avenues and the way the radial streets connect to the parks... its not just random planning. it looks like a specific geometric sigil. like a circuit. have u ever looked into the occult geometry behind the dc layout??",
