      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's just the surface level stuff. if you look at the way the streets curve specifically around the monuments, it's not just for \"navigation.\" it feels intentional, like they're steering people's movement or focus in a certain way. i feel like there's a reason why the angles are so specific. can you look at the pattern of the radiating avenues more closely? i feel like there's a deeper mathematical structure there that isn't just about efficiency.",
